                  </hi>. These coins are bad, but from different moulds.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The Prisoner produced a written defence, stating that he was playing at domi<lb></lb>noes, and having to pay</hi> 4<hi rend="italic">d. got the coins in change for a half-crown</hi>. <hi rend="smallCaps">
